Champions League
Champions League: the canvas ignites for this crazy night
Party crazy in the Champions League with incredible reversals of situation but also the confirmation of the return in form of the OL, the fall of Lille ...
05 Nov 2019, 22:16 by Antoine Chirat

Eight games on the program including a magnificent Chelsea - Ajax Amsterdam, the comeback form of Olympique Lyonnais, Lille that collapses after leading 1-0 ... an evening that has not failed to react the canvas that took the opportunity to ignite!
